title: Lack of diversity in the Libyan parliament : percentage of minority representation
summary: This chart looks at Lack in the Libyan by looking at the percentage of minority during four year periods .
The overall trend is an increase in percentage minority from 1990 to 2019 .
During the period 1990 - 1994 there was 0.4 percentage minority .
gold: In 2015 - 2019 , lack of diversity rose to 14 % . This is the highest in recent years . In 1990 - 1994 , lack of diversity in Libyan parliament was highly below 2 % .
